---
title: Middle Eastern Falafel & Roast Cauliflower Salad with Lemon Yoghurt & Pickled Onion
description: Hearty falafel bites are the stars of this Middle Eastern feast, and our technique of breaking them up before frying ensures they become
crisp and golden. With zingy pickled onion to brighten the flavours plus spiced roasted veggies, this is all the good stuff!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-falafel-roast-veggies-c46501c1.jpg
